<HEADLINE>
<P>
BARGAIN WOODSTOCK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 You can spend hundreds of dollars to attend Woodstock '94 Aug. 12-14, or you 
can stay home and watch the Red Hot Chili Peppers (Anthony Kiedis, left) and 
other acts on pay-per-view for $49.95. To experience Virtual Woodstock, get 
into a traffic jam that weekend and build a mud pit in your yard. 
</P>
