(20th Century Fox) $27.5 $10,925 2. "Forrest Gump" $24.1 2,024 2 (Paramount) 
$72.1 $11,979 3. "The Lion King" $16.9 2,624 5 (Walt Disney) $174.3 $6,435 4. 
