$5.1 1,903 6 (20th Century Fox) $93.5 $2,682 6. "I Love Trouble" $3.4 1,633 3 
(Disney/Touchstone) $23 $2,060 7. "Blown Away" $2.5 1,862 3 (MGM) $23.8 $1,360 
8. "The Shadow" $2.47 1,671 3 (Universal) $24.7 $1,480 9. "Wolf" $2.1 1,752 5 
(Columbia ) $59.4 $1,201 10. "The Flintstones" $1.4 1,298 8 (Universal) $119.5 
$1,105 SOURCE: Exhibitor Relations Co. DAVID J. FOX 
</P>
