<DOCNO> LA071994-0043 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 061964 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 19, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition Correction Appended 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
World Report; Page 2; Column 1; World Report 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
