</P>
<P>
 La Habra: two council 
</P>
<P>
 Lake Forest: three council 
</P>
<P>
 La Palma: two council 
</P>
<P>
 Los Alamitos: three council 
</P>
<P>
 Mission Viejo: three council 
</P>
<P>
