</P>
<P>
 Orange: two council 
</P>
<P>
 Placentia: two council 
</P>
<P>
 San Clemente: three council 
</P>
<P>
 San Juan Capistrano: three council 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Ana: mayor, three council 
</P>
<P>
 Stanton: three council 
</P>
<P>
