 Razor wire had been pulled off the top of a nine-foot fence that surrounds the 
minimum security area where Arroyo was held, Ramirez said. 
</P>
<P>
 Arroyo was arrested May 28 and had been scheduled to be released Oct. 9. 
DOUGLAS ALGER 
</P>
