<DOCNO> LA071994-0222 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 062143 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 19, 1994, Tuesday, Valley Edition 
</P>
