</P>
<P>
 The Ventura County Board of Education will hear the opinion of the Ventura 
County Counsel on whether Supt.Charles Weis acted within his authority when he 
terminated Dan Flynn's contract effective July 1. 
</P>
<P>
 The county board will meet at 5 p.m. today in the new offices of the county 
Superintendent of Schools at 5189 Verdugo Way in Camarillo. 
</P>
