<P>
 A 35-year-old Newbury Park woman was killed after the car she was riding in 
struck a parked car, authorities said Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 Donna Tognetti died of massive internal injuries at Los Robles Regional 
Medical Center at 6:45 p.m. Sunday, about two hours after her companion, 
Michael Rowland, lost control of the car he was driving in a Newbury Park 
residential neighborhood, authorities said. 
</P>
