fajitas/flour tortillas 839 24 1,526 with beans, rice, sour cream, guacamole 
1,661 63 3,657 * Beef burrito 833 40 1,965 with beans, rice, sour cream, 
guacamole 1,639 79 3,921 * Cheese enchilada 372 24 635 Two enchiladas with 
beans, rice 1,349 68 2,878 * Chile relleno 487 38 872 Two chile rellenos with 
beans, rice 1,578 96 3,352 * Taco salad with sour cream, guacamole 1,099 71 
1,847 SOURCE: Center for Science in the Public Interest  
</P>
</TEXT>
