<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 California League -- Hank Stickney is the owner of the Rancho Cucamonga 
Quakes, not Ken Stickney as was reported in Sunday's editions. Ken Stickney, 
Hank's son, owns the Lake Elsinore Storm. 
</P>
